sequenceDiagram
    participant Node
    participant Gateway
    participant NS as Network Server
    participant AS as Application Server

    Note over Node,NS: NwkSKey (MIC Authentication)
    Note over Node,AS: AppSKey (AES-128 E2E Encryption)
    Node->>Gateway: Encrypted Payload
    Gateway->>NS: Encrypted Payload
    NS->>AS: Encrypted Payload (Decrypted by AS)
